Great movie and great quality. The only complaint I really have is when there are subtitles for foreign languages, they're not in English (think it's Russian but can't be sure). But these scenes are few and far between and you can follow the plot perfectly without understanding the subtitles in these brief scenes. 

If you're in an area where it's not in the theaters yet (like I am, won't be out for quite some time where I'm at), then this is a great download. But when it does come out in theaters, I definitely encourage you to go see it again.

Also, this torrent doesn't include the additional scene after the credits. But there are other torrents for that. I suggest you track it down, because it's awesome.
